    "Additionally, dependencies of the code samples are extracted, i.e., submodules of multi-module code samples are identified and recorded as metadata to facilitate research on techniques such as few-shot learning and RAG for generating multi-module Verilog code.2) Description Generation: Natural language descriptions are appended to the code samples using an approach similar to VerilogEval [8], leveraging LLMs' superior natural language generation capabilities.",
